            "description": "<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 0cm; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">On 1 September 2024, between 11 AM &ndash; 12 noon (local time), a twister (tornado) struck across a community in Jaluit atoll.&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 0cm; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">A total of 5 households (21 people) were directly affected by the twister and are displaced. The displaced people are now living with neighbours. </span>The total population in the Jaluit atoll is 1,409 people (female: 688/ male: 721).</li>\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 0cm; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">5 houses were affected, 4 with severe roof damage. The water catchment system was completely destroyed, and the sanitation facilities was also damaged.</span></li>\n</ul>",
            "summary": "MHL: Other - 09-2024 - Tornado: Jaluit Atoll",
            "translation_module_original_language": "en"
          }
