"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Segoe UI',sans-serif; color: #374151;\">NOAA staff indicate the possibility of more extensive damage than the December 2008 flood event in the RMI, comparable to the December 2021 King Tide inundation event across the FSM.</span></p>\r\n</div>",
